data.description: Centrally located remodeled home with easy living floor plan, beautiful back covered porch with privacy fencing along with a 24' x 42' drive through shop garage that has 2-16'x8' high garage doors, insulated, sheet-rock and overhead gas heat. This home has been remodeled top to bottom.  New trim, interior and exterior doors, updated cabinets, new concrete countertops, tile bathrooms, refinished wood floors, new flooring, new windows, etc. The seller has replace the exterior concrete and has it stamped to show off how nice concrete can look. Very nicely done, must see in person to appreciate.
